parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Alternator failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or strandings. It can also cause electrical system failures, including the failure of essential systems like the brakes, steering, and lights.
symptoms: The alternator warning light on the dashboard
burning smell or smoke from the engine compartment
dim or flickering headlights
difficulty starting the engine
and sudden loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause a range of problems, including loss of power, stalling, and failure of essential systems like the brakes, steering, and lights.
symptoms: Warning lights on the dashboard
loss of power
stalling
difficulty starting the engine
and failure of electrical systems like the radio
lights
and wipers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Hands-free module failure can cause problems with the vehicle's infotainment system, including the loss of phone connectivity and audio functionality.
symptoms: Failure of the hands-free phone system
inability to connect to the vehicle's Bluetooth system
and loss of audio functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or shift abruptly, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission shifts funny
jolts during shifting
hesitates to shift gear
loses power
or fails to shift out of park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or fail to shift gears, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or fail to function properly, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system fails
causing the battery power to decrease
the alternator to fail
or the computer to lock up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Suspension failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The suspension fails
causing the CV joints to fail
the struts to fail
or the rocker arms to fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag warning light flashes
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of a crash
the seat belt tensioner fails to deploy
the side curtain airbags fail to deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing the airbag system can lead to the continued risk of airbag failure, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag warning light flashes
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of a crash
the seat belt tensioner fails to deploy
the side curtain airbags fail to deploy
the recall repair is delayed or unavailable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the instrument panel can affect the deployment of the passenger airbag, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The leather wrap on the instrument panel delaminates
the passenger airbag may not deploy properly.
